Deathrun_Stygian is a new map I started working on a few months ago, but I lost interest and stopped mapping for a while. A few weeks ago I finally got my thumb out of my ass and decided to finish it.

It still need some optimization, but since I suck at that I will leave it for now.


There are 15 traps and 3 ends on the map.
